National Timber Company, Plaintiff in Error, v. T. J. Diamond, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Escambia. Blount cG Blount cG Garter, for Plaintiff in Error; E. D. Beggs, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for defendant in error.
